The '''Sabiador Slavers''' were one of the largest [[Slavery/Legends|slaving]] operators during the [[Galactic Civil War/Legends|Galactic Civil War]], operating in and around the [[Kathol sector/Legends|Kathol sector]]. They were destroyed during the [[Battle of Kathol System]] between [[Moff/Legends|Moff]] [[Kentor Sarne]] and the crew of the ''[[FarStar]]''.

One-time members of the Slavers were the [[Human/Legends|Human]] [[Uta T'Cha]] and the [[Rodian/Legends|Rodian]] [[Gorak Khzam]].

